{"tid":1875492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰(00293.HK)：工會未獲足夠會員投票支持罷工行動 航班將如常運作","createTime":"2020-02-11T21:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T06:33:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa61bd2d5f66d5ab6fbac07fee575178b9d0ffb","tid":1875492,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T21:24:22.000Z","msg":"國泰(<a href=\"http://00293.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00293.HK&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=ab00c521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00293.HK</a>)公布，知悉工會未獲足夠會員投票支持罷工行動。國泰港龍目前的航班服務運作如常，預計將不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n此外，集團指即使目前的環境十分艱難，國泰作為航空公司，有責任維持香港與世界各地的重要聯繫。故此，集團仍維持少部分經審慎安排的國泰港龍航班服務來往中國內地，與此同時會嚴格遵守健康與安全準則，以確保其員工與顧客的健康安全。"},{"pid":"f02b61467fb8176c45c30caef5be21157d3bedd6","tid":1875492,"uid":52897,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T21:33:51.000Z","msg":"唔意外，佢地如果肯罷工，幾個月前都罷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962630886e1eae0af3be85e8a5788095917e8ba4","tid":1875492,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f02b61467fb8176c45c30caef5be21157d3bedd6","tid":1875492,"uid":52897,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T21:33:51.000Z","msg":"唔意外，佢地如果肯罷工，幾個月前都罷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T21:35:42.000Z","msg":"英國研究<br />\n大陸製造<br />\n南韓起源<br />\n台灣報導<br />\n香港罷工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019038b2113d446d823fd156d6a8835617f7c6f7","tid":1875492,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T21:36:13.000Z","msg":"佢而家擺都失去左最佳時機<br />\n做乜唔孖醫護一齊罷"},{"pid":"e18542a581ba1cbafc4a533631f4d890ad5e2b46","tid":1875492,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"019038b2113d446d823fd156d6a8835617f7c6f7","tid":1875492,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"